org.jamsim.ascape.navigator

Class OutputNode

  • java.lang.Object
    • DefaultScapeListener
      • org.jamsim.ascape.navigator.OutputNode

  • public class OutputNode
extends DefaultScapeListener
    A org.ascape.model.event.ScapeListener that displays Navigator output nodes after each iteration and/or at the end of the simulation. Nodes displayed are provided by a OutputNodeProvider.
    Version:
    $Revision$
    Author:
    Oliver Mannion
